        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Live adults of Cuban species of Calisto. A: C. herophile. B: C. torrei. C: C. bradleyi. D: C. disjunctus hersheyi. E: C. gundlachi. F: C. bruneri. G: C. sharkeyae. H: C. smintheus. I: C. israeli. J: C. lastrai. K: C. muripetens. L: C. occulta. M: C. brochei. N: C. dissimulatum. O: C. a. aquilum. P: C. aquilum occidentalis (worn individual). Photos by: Andy J. Corso (A), Rayner Núñez (B-C, F-I, K-P), Yosiel Álvarez (D-E) and Douglas M. Fernández (J)." ;
